le=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin-top: auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">4</span><span style=\"color: black; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">月</span></p></td><td width=\"156\" style=\"border-width: medium 1px 1px medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">4.1</span></p></td><td width=\"168\" style=\"border-width: medium 1px 1px medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">11.3</span></p></td><td width=\"156\" style=\"border-width: medium 1px 1px medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">11</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"55\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin-top: auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">5</span><span style=\"color: black; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">月</span></p></td><td width=\"156\" style=\"border-width: medium 1px 1px medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">5.3</span></p></td><td width=\"168\" style=\"border-width: medium 1px 1px medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; padding: 0px